Subject: Worker Job

& [WorkerJob_lm_studio_local_model] is a turn-spool worker record
  + [worker_id] is lm_studio_local_model
  + [lane] is lm_studio_cli
  + [objective] is Local model reflection lane through LM Studio-compatible API.
  + [status] is blocked
  + [prompt_packet] is prompt.md
  + [launch_command] is blocked: LM Studio launch policy not configured
  + [result_file] is result.sop
  + [attention_frame] is none
  = must: inspect launch_command before execution
  - never: infer completion from launch alone
